TITLE: Monitoring Connection Pool Acquisition Time
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of pool monitoring using Sequelize hooks to track connection acquisition time. Uses WeakMap to store timing data and logs the elapsed time for each connection acquisition.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sequelize/website/blob/main/docs/other-topics/connection-pool.md#2025-04-09_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const acquireAttempts = new WeakMap();

sequelize.hooks.addListener('beforePoolAcquire', options => {
  acquireAttempts.set(options, Date.now());
});

sequelize.hooks.addListener('afterPoolAcquire', _connection, options => {
  const elapsedTime = Date.now() - acquireAttempts.get(options);
  console.log(`Connection acquired in ${elapsedTime}ms`);
});
```

