TITLE: Manual Foreign Key References Without Constraints
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to manually define foreign key references between models without using association constraints. This approach defines relationships explicitly in the model definitions using the references property in column definitions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sequelize/website/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-6.x.x/other-topics/constraints-and-circularities.md#2025-04-09_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
