TITLE: Generated SQL for Junction Table Filtering in Sequelize
DESCRIPTION: Shows the SQL generated by Sequelize when filtering on junction table attributes in a Many-to-Many relationship eager loading query, illustrating how the conditions are applied to the join.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sequelize/website/blob/main/versioned_docs/version-6.x.x/advanced-association-concepts/eager-loading.md#2025-04-09_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: sql
